  'concept:compound-identity',
  'compound-identity',
  'concept',
  'Concept',
  'Compound identity record',
  'Data provenance',
  'A local chemistry record that distinguishes human-readable names from machine identifiers such as CID, InChIKey, SMILES and CAS number. | name + identifier + structure + source link -> citable identity | At least one public identifier and a source link should be retained for reproducibility.',
  '',
  'Data provenance',
  '',
  0,
  '',
  '[]',
  'record.html?type=concept&id=compound-identity',
  'library.html?q=Compound%20identity%20record',
  'https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/rest/pug/compound/name/Compound%20identity%20record/PNG?record_type=2d&image_size=large',
  '{"id":"compound-identity","term":"Compound identity record","family":"Data provenance","equation":"name + identifier + structure + source link -> citable identity","definition":"A local chemistry record that distinguishes human-readable names from machine identifiers such as CID, InChIKey, SMILES and CAS number.","academicUse":"Use it before comparing literature, spectra or safety data for a compound with multiple synonyms.","evidenceNote":"At least one public identifier and a source link should be retained for reproducibility.","sourceRefs":["pubchem","iupac-goldbook"]}',
  'concept concept compound identity record data provenance a local chemistry record that distinguishes human-readable names from machine identifiers such as cid inchikey smiles and cas number. name + identifier + structure + source link - citable identity at least one public identifier and a source link should be retained for reproducibility. data provenance definition a local chemistry record that distinguishes human-readable names from machine identifiers such as cid inchikey smiles and cas number. equation name + identifier + structure + source link - citable identity evidence note at least one public identifier and a source link should be retained for reproducibility.'
);
