  'concept:reaction-system-record',
  'reaction-system-record',
  'concept',
  'Concept',
  'Reaction system record',
  'Research informatics',
  'A structured record that treats a reaction as an evidence-bearing system rather than a single named transformation. | substrates + catalyst + conditions + readouts + failure modes -> defensible reaction claim | A complete record should include negative outcomes and impurity hypotheses, not just isolated yield.',
  '',
  'Research informatics',
  '',
